{"tid":541262,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，有無人係中意食南瓜","createTime":"2018-01-26T08:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T06:23:11.000Z","uid":5949,"like":27,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"084508132f2ae0fa6eb9de0d06b7de7bd92234d4","tid":541262,"uid":5949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"邊個發現南瓜係可以食嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚柒鳩難食嘅嘢都會放入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf600fa45276adf0a50f7892dde5483986efc85","tid":541262,"uid":5949,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"得罪講句食南瓜嘅全部都係辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575d586fd4ce1ddde4573fd4f7e82e698c39c692","tid":541262,"uid":42734,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"我鐘意"},{"pid":"188cbd075e0f0c885764243f2de23fbe148db9dd","tid":541262,"uid":6251,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"係外國人眼中，南瓜根本係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n每逢萬聖節，外國人都會用南瓜製作成雕刻<br />\n裝作成應節一個習俗。<br />\n<br />\n實際上西方國家的人只是希望以一個較好的籍口把南瓜掉棄<br />\n以美化浪費食物的行為<br />\n由於南瓜本來就是較容易生長，在農業社會時西方國家別無選擇才會種植南瓜<br />\n但當科技發達，資料豐富後<br />\n沒有人再願意食用南瓜，但為了保存種植南瓜的農民的生計，才一直生產<br />\n因此，西方國家便以萬聖節為籍口，將南瓜浪費掉，免得胃口受罪。"},{"pid":"a795c1d7e613e9d29a93ad5f86b4a99878ec0a5e","tid":541262,"uid":47647,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"南瓜蕃茄薯仔湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6973cd2cd06eda0f64c941da15250dbb9eaf4a15","tid":541262,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d211c59184af804154e0074e126ad334aba0720e","tid":541262,"uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T1